      <title>随着安全风险的增加，国际奥委会对法国当局对巴黎奥运会“充满信心”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/ioc-has-full-confidence-in-paris-olympic-games-as-security-risks-grow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际奥委会表示，在全球对以色列与哈马斯冲突的抗议活动日益增多的背景下，它对法国当局确保2024年巴黎奥运会顺利举行的能力“充满信心”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/ioc-has-full-confidence-in-paris-olympic-games-as-security-risks-grow</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 12:53:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
