      <title>加沙抗议投票影响英国工党选举进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/labour-s-uk-election-gains-curbed-by-gaza-protest-votes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党在英格兰和威尔士地方选举中的强劲表现受到削弱，因为一些穆斯林人口众多的地区的选民似乎不再支持反对党对加沙战争的立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/labour-s-uk-election-gains-curbed-by-gaza-protest-votes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 08:45:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
